message.body: Hey! Just a heads up, you're not in my schedule for tonight. -Liza
Oh I thought I was.. Is someone else there?
I went ahead and reserved so I must have missed this week
Yeah someone is. We could either not meet until next week or meet this weekend
No worries! it happens :) Do you still not have anything due? Can you meet this weekend?
Yeah I could! But do ya have time for that?
Yeah! My thesis is due Friday so I'm good for the weekend...just not before
Omg! We could have a party!
Oh my suite is having a wine and cheese/pizza and beer regatta Friday night
